v1SalesConfigInputs.description:
SalesConfigInputs are passed *into* some RPCs.  The boolean values for each
setting can be omitted.  This allows markets to only partially override the
partner-level settings.  Any omitted values should fall back to the partner-
level setting.

booleans.  The server will have to infer the boolean value of each setting if
it was absent when the sales configuration was set.

v1SubscriptionTierUpdateType.description:
- SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_FREE_TO_PAID: For going from the free tier to a paid VBP2 tier
 - SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_SWITCH_FREE_TRIAL: For selecting a new tier during the free trial period of a paid tier to another valid paid tier that allows free trials.
 - SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_CANCEL_FREE_TRIAL: For canceling the your free trial of a paid tier, the only valid tier to input is the free tier.
 - SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_CANCEL_FREE_TRIAL_FAILED_PAYMENT: For canceling the your free trial of a paid tier after a failed payment, the only valid tier to input is the free tier.
Also suspends the partners contract.
 - SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_FREE_TO_FREE_TRIAL: For going from the free tier to a free trial
 - SUBSCRIPTION_TIER_UPDATE_TYPE_PAID_TO_PAID: For going from the paid tier to a paid tier
